description: 1 of 5 gorgeous, new construction condos on the Eastside! High end finishes throughout including maple hardwoods, a designer kitchen compete with solid surface coutertops, Jennaire appliances and cherry cabinets, and a spa-like bathroom with porcelain tile and cherry cabinets. Both bedrooms are complete with large, built-in closet organization systems. Units have monitored alarm systems and sprinkler systems. This unit is complete with deeded storage, large patio and one deeded parking spot!
